'From Squeak3.4beta of ''1 December 2002'' [latest update: #5166] on 7 January 2003 at 5:09:45 pm'!"Change Set:		serverDirFix-swDate:			7 January 2003Author:			Scott WallaceFixes error seen when changing sort order in a file list for a server directory that had no file selected"!!FileList methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'sw 1/7/2003 17:08'!fullName	"Answer the full name for the currently selected file; answer nil if no file is selected."	^ fileName ifNotNil: [directory		ifNil:			[FileDirectory default fullNameFor: fileName]		ifNotNil:			[directory fullNameFor: fileName]]! !